content.detailedDescription:
Friday morning 1/31/14 at approx. 3:45am i was awake in my living room
and i began to hear a very low and loud hum coming from somewhere, so i stepped outside to try and find out what it was... to give you an idea of how loud it was, i have a service connected disability from the marine corps which is "hearing loss" and i did not have my hearing aids in my ears during this time. however, it was loud enough that ir caused a slight vibration all through my home as well as outside.

when i stepped outside i noticed that it was directly over my head !   however, it was very cloudy and whatever it was, was just above the low cloud cover.  i hurried inside to get my camera expecting it to appear under the clouds at any moment.

i stood there for another 4 or 5 minutes listening to it and trying to decide whether or not to call the sheriff's department since they took my summer sighting so lightly. i decided to wake my wife and as i was walking toward the door i noticed it getting quieter so i stopped and listened.

it slowly got quieter and quieter until it was gone. i suppose whatever it was ascended straight up because the sound stayed directly over my head... i also noticed my two labrador dogs and my cats were alert and observing the sound also.

later in the morning around 7-8am three u.S. blackhawk helecopters flew over. i wouldn't think that to be strange if we ever see military helecopters around here, but we don't... we are over a hundred miles from any military base and never see any military aircraft in this area. i am in the country and surrounded only by farm crops and old order amish folks. there is nothing out here.

i have no idea what this was, but something with a very low and very loud hum hovered over my property for about 7 or 9 minutes on friday morning at approximately 3:45 am.
content.summary: Only sound directly above me... no visible description.

content.detailedDescription: I saw a set of very multi-colored lights in a line changing color and moving slowly above the treetops. they moved from east to west for a few seconds then just disappeared. i've never seen any plane that color. and just disappeared. i watched for. a hour in the cold trying to see it again.
content.summary: Muti-colored bright lights.

content.detailedDescription: As i drove to work i noticed a strange site.  i first thought it might be a plane but it wasn't moving.  i watched out the front window of my car thinking it might just be moving slow. as i neared my destination i thought, "why is no one else paying attention to this".  it was shaped wide in the front, with 2 large 'headlights' that resembled that of a car.  two red lights (like parking lights) on the side.  i continued to keep an eye on it while i pulled out my phone in hopes of capturing a picture.  the craft stayed in place until i pulled in the lot to park. for a brief moment, i could not see the craft as my direction i parked, blocked it.  i hurried, put the car in park and jumped out to photograph the craft.  it was gone.  i searched the skys for it, the only thing i noticed was a "plane" on the other side of the sky.  then today my coworker said 2 birds fell out of the sky, one behind the other, while he was walking in the same place i parked.  hmmmm.  weather gone crazy, what's really going on?
content.summary: Observed strange craft hovering. didn't see it move.  went to take picture after i parked.  gone

content.detailedDescription: We were home at the time and we heard there was a meteorite shower in the sky that night. when we looked out we saw a multi-colored orb hovering in the southern part of the sky. it hovered for a awhile (approximately 2-3 minutes) then traveled to the northern part of the sky on the opposite side of our home and hovered there, it kept going back and forth a couple times hovering. i remember feeling very confused and vulnerable like we were being threatened. after that it traveled to the opposite side of the house when we looked out the window it was gone.
content.summary: Multi-colored orb in sky approx. size of 'moon' in sky hovered over household traveling south to north

content.detailedDescription: My husband first came to me one late evening, in early january. he's always really been into ufo's to where i'm more skeptical. he noticed it one evening looking out a bedroom window, slightly above a neighbors house. he noticed it's multi-color, flashing lights. when he asked me to look, i grabbed our video camera that has a really good zoom, hoping to get a closer look. when i zoomed in, i noticed a unusual cigar shape that appears to have lights or windows. it continues to be there in the sky, most nights. it's not always there, and weather has nothing to do with it. we would just like to get to the bottom if it, and find out what it really is.
content.summary: Flashing orb/ stationary. when zoomed in on with camera, cigar shaped.

content.detailedDescription: Driving south on rt. 169.  2 pm  on a monday afternoon. saw luminous disc shape object hover over tree top in low meadow. wife at time also remarked what's that? looked like 25-30 ft. disc outlined in thin silver or metallic with gold plasma like interior. watched clearly for minute than trees intermittently blocked out. passed state of ct. highway workers who were raking and had their backs turned toward object..Wanted to turn around to make them see object but decided to race to butts bridge road to packer road to see object over yaworski landfill(dump).When we got there i recognized tree it was over. disc was gone. tried to convince ourselves it was some sort of gas emitted from landfill. never told anyone but cpl law enforcement friends off the record...In 1989 these sightings weren't taken seriously.
content.summary: Returning from morning golf  viewed object in low meadow

content.summary: Bright light yellow or orange

content.detailedDescription: While driving home from work at 2340 hours on 01/03/14 i was driving south on terry plains road in simsbury. i immediately saw bright lights on my right front side above a wooded area close to the farmington river. i thought the lights were from a plane from a distance because its only about 10 miles to the bdl airport and a few miles to simsbury airport from there. but i was driving and noticed that the lights weren't moving. then i thought it might be a helicopter or some kind of search lights. it is very dark in that area at night and it's really hard to see anything in that area so the bright lights really stood out. but as i got closer i thought that it may be some kind of tower lights. but i quickly realized that there is no towers in that area. the lights i saw were extremely bright. there were three white lights and one center red light in a triangular formation. as i drove closer within 300 feet from the object. i could see it hovering just above the trees. then as i got closer it moved slowly to my left front and slowly moved north as i was driving very slowly south. when i saw it move by me i realized that the object also had multiple white lights on the sides of the triangle as well. i didn't see those side lights because of the position the object was in initially when i came upon it and the brightness of the main three white lights. at this point i stopped my car and pulled into side street and decided to turn around and follow the object to get a better view. i fumbled for my phone camera but i was trying to drive, figure out what i was looking at and keep my eyes on the road all at the same time. now i was headed in the same direction as the object but couldn't see it because it was hidden behind the tree line. i thought i might see it again just up ahead a little in the opening were there are horse stables and a side road to stop my car. i opened the moon roof interior door to get a better view of the sky and as i turned on to the clearing by the horse stables it felt like it was right over my car. i looked up through my moon roof window and was startled so much that i remember saying out loud "it's right there". i felt as i "they" caught me watching them. at that point i didn't stick around to watch it any longer. when i arrived home i immediately drew a sketch of the object so that i wouldn't forget what it looked like. of course i didn't see any other car on the dark road in the area that night. but i have to believe that someone else must have seen the bright lights. there are many homes in that area up along the ridgeline.
content.summary: I saw a large low hovering triangular object with multiple bright white lights and one red light.

content.detailedDescription:
Please let me know what you think this is, i can not get anyone to verify!
picture was taken january 6, 2014, 9:03 in the morning. rural north morris, illinois 60450.
 my son called and said go outside and check out the sun.  it was -43 degree wind chill, so i went outside and snapped off a bunch of pictures very quickly with my phone.  i was outside maybe a minute and came back inside the house, and my grandson and i went through the pictures.  i was hoping to get great pictures of the dog sun!!
 you can see there is a bright light in all the pictures (at first we wondered what it was), but that was my phone lens. then, i came across the other two that had an additional spot, i zoomed in on that photo and found what i have sent you. went back outside to see if it was still there and snapped a few more (dog didn't want to go this time) but there was nothing there. 
 i did not hear or see this, only got pictures.  please let me know what you think, i can not find anybody to verify what it is. it was there and then gone in a matter of seconds without sound!! i hope you see 3 things: it farther out in the distance, it close above my house and the other that i don't know what it is depicting.  if you zoom in around the entire sky, i believe you see many (not sure).
thanks, hope i gave you all the info you will need.
content.summary: Sun dog day,-43 wind chill, snapped quickly, did not see or hear, found in pic

content.detailedDescription:
Approximately 9:30 pm we were on the way home to 684 thomasboro rd in carolina shores nc. while traveling south on longwood road and about mile past the town of longwwod a cylindrical object crossed in front of us heading toward myrtle beach area. it had a blue light that remained constant at one end of it and a white light at the other end that was constant white. there was no sound and we saw it for about 30 secs to a minute and i tried following it as i drove on longwood road and then turned right onto pealanding road but could not find it anymore. strangest thing i have ever seen. i sensed it could have been an aircraft of some sort, however there was no strobe to any light on it and i know that aircraft should have a strobe light. i am only coming forward in case there were others that saw what i saw. it was strange...
thanks
todd johnson
content.summary: Driving home and saw a cigar shaped craft with blue light on one end and white light on the other cross the sky in front of us just above treetop and made a turn toward the ocean and disappeared from site.

content.detailedDescription:
My mom noticed the bright light through the window and then retrieved her camera to photograph the object.  
she went outside to the front entryway and took several photos.  note that the digital photos have the wrong time on them as the camera does not have the time set correctly.

the object pulsates and changes shapes and colors.  it hovers and moves about in an area and has appeared at various times and places in different directions over the course of the last year.  
this time the object was just above the tree line at the top of lakeview mountain looking to the east from the viewing location in priest lake, idaho.
content.summary: My mother observed and photographed the ufo while visiting me in priest lake, id  we have both seen the object before on different occassions and in different directions.

content.detailedDescription:
I was in bed looking at a star when this thing shoot across my line of sight through a casement window. this was third triangle i have seen since 1977 but the other two had white lights and i saw the bottom of the craft from directly overhead. this craft had to have sideways for me to see the bottom surface. the lights delineated the shape but it was not clear enough to see if it blocked out stars as the last two times. 

this sighting was also the second i have seen through the same window at night. the other is in your files and was a white sphere rising from about twenty feet and then turning and following the tree line until it was out
of sight. 

my wife and i have now had a total of four sightings in 2013 and 2014:
1. a black sphere in the daytime for mary.
2. a white sphere for me at night near my house at about 20 feet horizontally and vertically.
3. both of us saw an orange/red pulsating sphere at night while walking about 8:30 pm.
4. the aforementioned sighting above.

this all happened since summer, 2013.
 
now add my triangle sightings over emmaus years ago at night and the same in 1977 in bethlehem, pa at night and you  get a total of six (seven if you count my wife's lone daytime sighting as a separate sighting). 

the lehigh valley is getting a lot of attention from whomever is in the sky.
content.summary: Fas moving equilateral triangle with lights blinking crossed line of sight of window.

content.detailedDescription: Last night at about 7:45pm est i was on my sun porch looking up at the stars as i was smoking a cigarette. i was looking up at the stars and noticed a formation of more than 20 objects traveling at a high speed from the south heading north. the formation was almost like birds form, kinda. they were orange-yellow-red in color. strangest thing i have ever seen.
content.summary: Formation

content.detailedDescription:
My sister and i were in steilacoom by the water across from mcneil island and tried looking at the moon with a telescope cause it was clear outside, then the moon disappeared behind the clouds. you can see the moon's glow behind the clouds. as i was folding my telescope up, a sphere looking object appeared and i put my telescope back together, i was focusing on the object then it slowly moved north and then it sort of disappeared as it would behind clouds, but there was no clouds around it. i thought it was the moon at first but we saw the white glow of the moon behind clouds still. 

it was slowly creeping north direction and then all of a sudden disappeared.
i was confused at what the object was and wondered what it was. i was a tad freaked out by it because i knew it wasn't the moon.
content.flightPath: Path with directional change,Path then hovering

content.detailedDescription: I was was setting on the couch watching t. v. when my girlfriends son yelled out ,hey come here and look. i got up and stepped to the door. what in the hell is that,i said,as it slowly went down behind the trees.  there where three bright white lights in a triangle going around slowly.  it was rotating about the same speed as it was descending. i did not know the owners of the land,witch was private property. that's the only reason i didn't investigate. i stayed up most of that nite watching for any further activity but there was none.We have talked about that nite often,it's a mistery!
content.summary: My girlfriends son said "hey ,what are those lights. i got up and we watched it go down behind the trees on to private property .

content.detailedDescription: As i was taking our two dogs out to the bathroom at 10:12 pm,cst. i noted how clear the sky was,no clouds ,fog or disturbance. the temp. outside was 1 *f above zero. i always look up to watch the stars and as i was doing so this time ,suddenly this time overhead,a brilliant white light very quickly appeared from the southeast,moved a short distance to the northwest and vanished. there was no sound,no airplanes in the area,no smoke trail,etc.The whole eppisode lasted approx. 1 1/2 to 2 seconds.
content.summary: Bright glowing  fast moving light

content.detailedDescription: At 5-13 am on jan 28th 2014 i stepped outside to start my car before going to work. i observed an object that had a bright red blinking light in the front a brilliant  blinking tungesten white light in the middle and a smaller white light to the end. my first thought was that this maybe a plane coming in to land at the calgary airport, but as it passed over it made no noise at all. i have seen many planes come into calgary and from my position i would say this object was much lower than i have seen any plane aproach before. if this was a plane it would have been about 3 times as long as a comercial jet. also i have never seen a plane with a red flasing light on the nose. it moved from the s.E. to the n.W., from my position it would have missed the airport by a good 15 miles. it maintained a steady altitude and speed and i watched it until it moved out of sight. i did have an uneasy feeling as it passed over me and felt some kind of pressure in my chest.
content.summary: Flashing red (1) and white (2) lights observed traveling in unison.

content.detailedDescription:
I was driving home from work on 23 south just after south bloomfield.  i was looking out the window at passing cars, just checking things out.  i noticed what i thought was the top of a tower light in an odd location.  as my car approached, my thought process went from tower light, to airplane, to "no it's stationary, maybe a helicopter with a search light?". 

once the three lights at each peak of the triangle was visible, it was clearly a triangle shaped something.  so i try to slow down to around 45, and yes, it is definitely a triangular shaped hovercraft-y aircraft of some sorts.  the lights lit up one by one, and then pulsated, more like, peaks and then troughs. once all the lights were lit, it glowed a bit stronger.  i was watching it - slash whipping my head back to the road - in quick intrivals for quite some time. 

so, naturally i get really excited, so i call someone to share the news, as i'm looking at it.  i talk to him until its out over my 'trying to drive while rubbernecking' perspective, and turn shortly after that to the court street entrance near sevan's.  i do a u-turn and look for it, but its gone.

i drove up to haggerty road and looked through the field and saw nothing.  afterwards, i continued home on the phone describing it, came home and drew a few sketches.  i proceed to do what anyone with internet does - i googled ufo sightings  and posted it here!
content.summary: A triangular shaped object with six lights pulsating and hovering over a field near haggerty road  a video and it was gone.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home from work and it was already dark. i saw a greenish bright object moving at a fast speed in the sky. it seemed to have a trail like a comet and for a split second the green ufo stopped in mid air. it exploded, or more precisely it seemed bigger for a split second, as if it had slow down or maybe everything slow down temporarily. then what seemed to be and smaller greenish flying object moved in what seemed like at an angle from initial trajectory. everything happened really fast and i was driving but it wad perfectly clear in the sky.
content.summary: Bright green ufo stopped in mid air exploded and smaller greenish flying object moved in what seemed like at an angle from initial trajectory.

content.detailedDescription: I was driving home after a business meeting at approximately 9:30 pm. deer mating season and i was on an unlighted highway so i was particularly alert. completely clear night with  no cloud cover.  i saw a glowing, pill shaped object fly by above me from due west to due east. the object was bright green and was visible for about 2 seconds before disappearing over the horizon. obviously moving at a high rate of speed. while not a  pilot or trained observer, i have served in the military  and can state without hesitation that the object was like nothing i have ever seen before. i immediately thought that i had just observed a ufo. i did not mention the incident to anyone, but have been unable to forget the incident , and felt that i should report this to you to determine if anyone else had seen this object. i might mention that incident occurred less than  3 miles from a nuclear assembly assembly plant, but does not have nuclear material on sight.
content.summary: Glowing bright green object passed over my vehicle at high rate of speed from west to east. clear night. shaped like a pill or hatbox.Ii

content.detailedDescription:
At around 9:50 pm of february 2nd, 2014. from my front door, i was seeing off a significant other after they were visiting. 

shortly after they had left, i saw these 3 stationary lights appear above mill hill, which is somewhere between 2-3 kilometers away from where i was standing and witnessing the event, and in a north-easterly direction. the lights appeared to be blinking with mixtures of yellows, whites, and golds in rapid succession. the craft did not move from its position above the small mountain, and only stayed in view in it's stationary position for about 2-3 minutes before appearing to "phase out of reality".

basing on the positioning of the lights in terms of shape, it's likely the craft could have been disk/saucer shaped or boomerang shaped. although, the darkness and distance made it hard to discern a specific shape aside from the positioning of the lights.
content.summary: 3 blinking stationary lights sighted over mill hill, before phasing out of reality.

content.detailedDescription: It was the fourth of july 2013 was relaxing in the back yard on lawn furniture around 4:30pm this object appeared moving west to east above tree line moving very slowly it was heading straight towards me it was flat black perfectly round object looked like it had one seam horizontally across with one slowly pulsating red light on lower half coming out of a square opening that seemed to be pointing towards its forward path as it moved ,that's when i stood up and was thinking what is this thing my mind was trying to adjust what it could be from a balloon to remote controlled device but it moved so persist and silent and when it came to property line of my back yard it changed its direction of path from heading east to south  that's when it was closest to me (120 feet away, estimated 10-15feet in size) i continued watching it till it disappeared by trees  no longer could see it.. felt like it was a drone type of device observing or monitoring the area ....
content.summary: Black ,round,1redlight moved silently above trees moving towards me then changed direction

content.detailedDescription:
A being who used the name "brennon" entered my apartment (or i entered it with him - unclear). he bumped my bed and said, "uh oh." i thought i was dreaming. 

a few minutes later, i woke up and noticed that my large key chain (with 15 keys) was missing from the pushpin in the wall. oddly, my wallet, which was directly below the keys, was not taken. 

for some reason, i was not really that upset (quite unlike me). fortunately, i had a duplicate set of most of the keys. i went to work. then, i came home and began looking for the keys. no luck. 

it was such an odd story that i did not want to file a police report. however, when i told the story to the assistant residence manager of my apartment complex a day later, she persuaded me to file a report. the officer came by, had me write out my story and photographed the area.

that night, i turned on my security system, made sure that the door was locked and went to bed. when i woke up the next morning, the keys were hanging from a pushpin in the wall.

there is no way that i (or the police officer) could have missed seeing the key chain. there is also no way that anyone could have broken into my apartment (through the door or windows) without the alarm system going off.

i laid down, relaxed. i then recalled that the being's name was brennon. although he is not, as i recall, from this planet, he lives here. he looks like an ordinary guy. i was sitting across from him at a large rectangular table. he was explaining to me what would happen. he made sure that i would not get up until after he was gone.

i took the account as a lesson to always keep the front door locked with the alarm system on (which i had not been doing).
content.summary: Contact experience - keys lost and then returned
